children.text: NOTICE: The application you are about to install is a fast, easy way to shop and explore products and services available from Sears Family of Businesses. In order to perform this function, the application will monitor, record, or otherwise access your communications between itself and the server(s) operated by or on behalf of the applicable Sears Holdings entity with which you are interacting. This application does not monitor, record, or transmit interactions with other 3rd party websites that are not part of the Sears Holdings Family of Businesses. The data monitored, recorded or stored by this application may include personal financial or health information to the extent you voluntarily provide that information to the application as you interact with our servers. For example, you may choose store your credit card on our servers or order prescriptions from Kmart Pharmacy through our Mobile Application. Such information is transmitted directly to our servers and is never stored on your mobile device. We use this information in order to provide you with the goods and services you request. Additionally, in order to improve our mobile product offerings, this application may track how you use the application, including the features, content, and specific pages within the application you visit. We use this analytical information to improve the application and your experience as you use it. The data we collect as you use this application may not be used by a third party except as may be permitted under our Privacy Policy, which you may review on the next screen and from within the application.
